timelineItems.desc:
For the third time in the past four World Cups, the defending champions failed to reach the knockout stage. Chile defeated Spain 2-0 on Wednesday, ending La Roja's chances at repeating as World Cup Champions. Relive the historic match in pictures.

Catch all of MLSsoccer.com's World Cup coverage at www.mlssoccer.com/worldcup
